  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help 100 Mexican Children Stay in Secondary School</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In response to the violence and drug war in our country, HECAT was opened in the Northern Mexican city of Torreon seeking to provide better chances to children from low-income families through high quality education.  With your help, this project will expand our middle school program by building three new rooms on our roof to continue to provide education, nutritional and medical support for children who hail from some of the poorest areas of our region.</narrative>
  </description>
